@1000009 = ~This was the fool trying to spy on us, exactly how we planned it. According to our information he is not too high up in the Zhentarim and we only needed him to get to his partner, who is hopefully dead as you read this. Make sure to dump his body far out in the sea, since we saw no need to take extra measures ensuring he won't come back.

